I don't know from where to start
Assalamu alaikum dear readers i am not from Hyderabad but for work related purpose i came so may times Hyderabad but this time my stay is at near kphb metro. So when i searched masjid near me this mosque pop upd as i came here. I was bit confused it was crowded (talking about fryday) my first day was fryday so after that i came specially for isha prayer and sometimes fazar too when i get free so...
As i started coming here the best thing about this masjid is Imams voice allahhu akbar cant explain this is just beautiful calming heart touching soothing and if you notice his voice is similar to the imam of the kaaba maher al muqaity.

Note : fryday prayer is at 1:30 pm
I got late due to someone told in review 1:40 so take care about this

featured_reviews.review_id:
I am shaik Nabesaheb from kodad, nalgonda distric and  I am staying in hyd for a job perpose since 8 months.I attended so many masjids for doing salah  (namaz). But I have never seen a mosque with such good facilities. also the recent whole ramzan i spent here, the committee accommodat sehar facility to all the hostel and Who can not prepare their food in the morning sehar(approximately 500 members and they provide daily non-veg, very good taste food, Surely every single one will definitely satisfied from that food).

The imaam sahab's speech and the way of explanation was definitely makes u feel good develop you deen  and wil be motivational, Also  his Qur'an recitation was very smooth and clear.

Especially on Fridays heavy crowd(Nearly 1500 members), It's best to do vazu from home, the timing of zuma namaz is 1:40, there is no excuse in timings.

You can donate to this masjid without thinking, they are used for  good  works perpose they didn't not misusing.

May Allah grant and accept who served, serving , helping, supporting, dedicated their Every small time and work for this masjid. .

featured_reviews.review_id: One of the spacious mosques in KPHB Colony. Located at a very peaceful area. This mosque serves as a place of worship to local residents and also many employees working in different malls and shops in the area. This masjid is jam packed on Fridays and in Ramadan. Alhamdulillah, very neat place and special arrangements are made during holy month of ramadan which helps hostel students a lot. Imam sahab is also a very good person and recites quran with a beautiful voice. I wish more and more people visit this mosque and donate generously for its continued maintenance. May Allah keep this masjid always aabaad with worshippers.
